---
// src/components/Contact.astro
---
<section id="contact" class="relative flex min-h-screen items-center bg-black py-32 text-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-slate-950 to-black"></div>
    <div class="absolute right-10 top-20 -z-10 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/30 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto flex max-w-5xl flex-col gap-12 px-6 lg:flex-row">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-purple-200">Contact</span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-5xl">Parlons de votre prochaine mission</h2>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
                Basé à Montseret (Aude), j’étudie votre besoin et organise une mission drone dans un rayon d’environ 135 km autour de Narbonne, couvrant notamment Carcassonne, Béziers et Toulouse.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 text-sm text-gray-300">
                <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5 backdrop-blur-xl">
                    <h3 class="text-white">Email direct</h3>
                    <a href="mailto:toffolon.mathieu11@gmail.com" class="mt-2 block text-lg font-semibold text-white">toffolon.mathieu11@gmail.com</a>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-400">Réponse sous 24h</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5 backdrop-blur-xl">
                    <h3 class="text-white">Téléphone</h3>
                    <a href="tel:+33781730114" class="mt-2 block text-lg font-semibold text-white">07 81 73 01 14</a>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-400">Devis & disponibilité</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5 backdrop-blur-xl">
                    <h3 class="text-white">Adresse</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">13 impasse des Aires, 11200 Montseret</p>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-400">Déplacements sur rendez-vous</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-purple-500/10 backdrop-blur-2xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Décrivez votre projet</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-300">Indiquez-nous la localisation, les échéances et les livrables visés pour recevoir un devis précis.</p>
            <form class="mt-6 space-y-5">
                <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                    <label class="flex flex-col text-sm text-gray-300">
                        Nom
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Entreprise / Nom" class="mt-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/50 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder:text-gray-500 focus:border-purple-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500/50" />
                    </label>
                    <label class="flex flex-col text-sm text-gray-300">
                        Email
                        <input type="email" placeholder="nom@domaine.com" class="mt-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/50 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder:text-gray-500 focus:border-purple-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500/50" />
                    </label>
                </div>
                <label class="flex flex-col text-sm text-gray-300">
                    Type de mission
                    <select class="mt-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/50 px-4 py-3 text-white focus:border-purple-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500/50">
                        <option class="bg-black" value="inspection">Inspection / toiture</option>
                        <option class="bg-black" value="cartographie">Cartographie légère / terrain</option>
                        <option class="bg-black" value="creative">Photo / vidéo immobilière</option>
                        <option class="bg-black" value="portrait">Portrait / projet personnel</option>
                        <option class="bg-black" value="autre">Autre besoin</option>
                    </select>
                </label>
                <label class="flex flex-col text-sm text-gray-300">
                    Détails supplémentaires
                    <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Zone d’intervention, contraintes, délais…" class="mt-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/50 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder:text-gray-500 focus:border-purple-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500/50"></textarea>
                </label>
                <button type="submit" class="w-full rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 via-fuchsia-500 to-indigo-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/20 transition hover:scale-[1.02]">Envoyer la demande</button>
                <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-400">En soumettant ce formulaire, vous acceptez que Stellaris Drone traite vos informations pour vous répondre. Aucune donnée n’est partagée avec des tiers.</p>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
